Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,彻底唤醒
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.19,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,一次次低语
